# Input

```scss
$foo:('property1':(),'property2':1,/** comment 1 */
/* comment 2 */
);

$bar:('property1':(),'property2':1,
/** comment 1 */
/* comment 2 */
);

$blank:('property1':(),'property2':1,/** comment 1 */

/* comment 2 */
);

$nested:(outer:(inner:value,),/** one */
/* two */);

```


# Formatted

```scss
$foo: (
	"property1": (),
	"property2": 1,
	/** comment 1 */ /* comment 2 */
);

$bar: (
	"property1": (),
	"property2": 1,
	/** comment 1 */ /* comment 2 */
);

$blank: (
	"property1": (),
	"property2": 1,

	/** comment 1 */ /* comment 2 */
);

$nested: (
	outer: (
		inner: value,
	),
	/** one */ /* two */
);

```
